of 30 different characters in each faction,

171
00:12:18,465 --> 00:12:21,727
and each character had their own custom stylized effects.

172
00:12:21,727 --> 00:12:26,191
So by creating this style guide,

173
00:12:26,191 --> 00:12:28,933
we were able to cement the look of each faction

174
00:12:28,933 --> 00:12:31,015
while still keeping each character's effects

175
00:12:31,015 --> 00:12:33,097
feeling uniquely their own.

176
00:12:33,097 --> 00:12:38,541
So for example, we had the Generate faction,

177
00:12:38,541 --> 00:12:40,683
which is in the bottom left.

